  <Content>There have been rumors of a giant creature on the outskirts of Mileth. Aingeal heard it from the beggar, Teague, in the Mileth Tavern a few suns ago; however, I wouldn't trust anything coming from that old run-down drunkard. 

Some of the farmers, though, are becoming concerned about their crops; this creature is said to be able to devour entire fields in the matter of moments! 

Im not going to get all caught up in it, but you may want to see what he has to say. Teague does have a tendency to be right about these things.

Riona
Mileth Innkeeper

